SELECT COALESCE("DISPLAYNAME", "DISPLAYNAME") AS "DISPLAYNAME", "REPUTATION", "POSTCOUNT", "QUESTIONCOUNT", "ANSWERCOUNT", "ACCEPTEDANSWERS", "POPULARPOSTS", "BADGECOUNT", "GOLDBADGES", "SILVERBADGES", "BRONZEBADGES"
FROM (SELECT "t1"."USERID", "t1"."DISPLAYNAME", "t1"."REPUTATION", "t1"."POSTCOUNT", "t1"."QUESTIONCOUNT", "t1"."ANSWERCOUNT", "t1"."ACCEPTEDANSWERS", "t1"."POPULARPOSTS", CASE WHEN "t3"."BADGECOUNT" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."BADGECOUNT" AS BIGINT) ELSE 0 END AS "BADGECOUNT", CASE WHEN "t3"."GOLDBADGES" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."GOLDBADGES" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "GOLDBADGES", CASE WHEN "t3"."SILVERBADGES" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."SILVERBADGES" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "SILVERBADGES", CASE WHEN "t3"."BRONZEBADGES" IS NOT NULL THEN CAST("t3"."BRONZEBADGES" AS INTEGER) ELSE 0 END AS "BRONZEBADGES"
FROM (SELECT ANY_VALUE("Users"."Id") AS "USERID", "Users"."DisplayName" AS "DISPLAYNAME", "Users"."Reputation" AS "REPUTATION", COUNT(DISTINCT "Posts"."Id") AS "POSTCOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Posts"."PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "QUESTIONCOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Posts"."PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "ANSWERCOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Posts"."PostTypeId" AS INTEGER) = 1 AND "Posts"."AcceptedAnswerId" IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "ACCEPTEDANSWERS", SUM(CASE WHEN "Posts"."ViewCount" > 100 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "POPULARPOSTS"
FROM "STACK"."Users"
LEFT JOIN "STACK"."Posts" ON "Users"."Id" = "Posts"."OwnerUserId"
GROUP BY "Users"."Id", "Users"."DisplayName", "Users"."Reputation") AS "t1"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "UserId" AS "USERID", COUNT(*) AS "BADGECOUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Class" AS INTEGER) = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "GOLDBADGES", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Class" AS INTEGER) = 2 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "SILVERBADGES", SUM(CASE WHEN CAST("Class" AS INTEGER) = 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS "BRONZEBADGES"
FROM "STACK"."Badges"
GROUP BY "UserId") AS "t3" ON "t1"."USERID" = "t3"."USERID") AS "t4"
WHERE "t4"."REPUTATION" > 1000 AND "t4"."POSTCOUNT" > 10